        "text": "=Account data:\nCompany: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.company }}\nTrigger: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.triggerEvent.description }}\nCoverage: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.coverageLabel }}\nEngaged Members: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.engagedRoles }}\nSignals: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.allWeightedSignals }}\n\nEngine decision (use as the move, do not re-decide):\nStage: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.when_stage }}\nUrgency: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.when_urgency }}\nRecommended move: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.when_the_move }}\nOpen with: {{ $('Loop Over Items').first().json.when_open_with }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a B2B sales brief writer. The WHEN engine has ALREADY decided the move; your job is to write the brief that delivers it — do not re-decide. Under 150 words. Six elements exactly:\n\n1. Trigger Event — what happened and when\n2. Account Context — company, industry, competitive situation\n3. Opening Hypothesis — why this account, why now\n4. Stage-Designated Action — the engine's recommended move\n5. Buying Group Indicator — who is engaged, coverage label\n6. Signal Return — what to watch for next"
        }
